Package noteApp.model.note

Class Archiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • noteApp.model.note.Archiver
  • public class Archiver
extends java.lang.Object
    Note archiver class which adds or removes special characters from notes' titles. Characters are used to show either normal notes or archived notes on the view.
    Author:
    Matias Vainio

      • archiveNote

        public void archiveNote​(Note selectedNote)
        Archives provided note by appending '%a' to the start note's title. '%a' is used to check which notes are going to be showed on the view. Updates the view.
        Parameters:
        selectedNote - provided note which is going to be modified.

        public void returnFromArchive​(Note selectedNote)
